[
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " “Now, listen, Jacob my servant,"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "Israel whom I have chosen!”"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " This is what "
  },
  {
    "type": "divine_name",
    "value": "YHWH"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": ", the one who made you, says – "
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "the one who formed you in the womb and helps you:"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "“Don’t be afraid, my servant Jacob,"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "Jeshurun,"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " whom I have chosen!"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " For I will pour water on the parched ground"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "and cause streams to flow"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " on the dry land."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "I will pour my spirit on your offspring"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "and my blessing on your children."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " They will sprout up like a tree in the grass,"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "like poplars beside channels of water."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " One will say, ‘I belong to "
  },
  {
    "type": "divine_name",
    "value": "YHWH"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": ",’"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "and another will use"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " the name ‘Jacob.’"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "One will write on his hand, ‘"
  },
  {
    "type": "divine_name",
    "value": "YHWH"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "’s,’"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "and use the name ‘Israel.’”"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " This is what "
  },
  {
    "type": "divine_name",
    "value": "YHWH"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": ", Israel’s king, says,"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "their protector,"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " "
  },
  {
    "type": "divine_name",
    "value": "YHWH"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " who commands armies:"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "“I am the first and I am the last,"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "there is no God but me."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " Who is like me? Let him make his claim!"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "Let him announce it and explain it to me – "
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "since I established an ancient people – "
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "let them announce future events!"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " Don’t panic! Don’t be afraid!"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "Did I not tell you beforehand and decree it?"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "You are my witnesses! Is there any God but me?"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "There is no other sheltering rock;"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " I know of none."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " All who form idols are nothing;"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "the things in which they delight are worthless."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "Their witnesses cannot see;"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "they recognize nothing, so they are put to shame."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " Who forms a god and casts an idol"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "that will prove worthless?"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " Look, all his associates"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " will be put to shame;"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "the craftsmen are mere humans."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "Let them all assemble and take their stand!"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "They will panic and be put to shame."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " A blacksmith works with his tool"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "and forges metal over the coals."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "He forms it"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " with hammers;"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "he makes it with his strong arm."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "He gets hungry and loses his energy;"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "he drinks no water and gets tired."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " A carpenter takes measurements;"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "he marks out an outline of its form;"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "he scrapes"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " it with chisels,"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "and marks it with a compass."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "He patterns it after the human form,"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "like a well-built human being,"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "and puts it in a shrine."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " He cuts down cedars"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "and acquires a cypress"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " or an oak."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "He gets"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " trees from the forest;"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "he plants a cedar"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " and the rain makes it grow."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " A man uses it to make a fire;"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "he takes some of it and warms himself."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "Yes, he kindles a fire and bakes bread."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "Then he makes a god and worships it;"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "he makes an idol and bows down to it."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " Half of it he burns in the fire – "
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "over that half he cooks"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " meat;"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "he roasts a meal and fills himself."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "Yes, he warms himself and says,"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "‘Ah! I am warm as I look at the fire.’"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " With the rest of it he makes a god, his idol;"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "he bows down to it and worships it."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "He prays to it, saying,"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "‘Rescue me, for you are my god!’"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " They do not comprehend or understand,"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "for their eyes are blind and cannot see;"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "their minds do not discern."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " No one thinks to himself,"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "nor do they comprehend or understand and say to themselves:"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "‘I burned half of it in the fire – "
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "yes, I baked bread over the coals;"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "I roasted meat and ate it."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "With the rest of it should I make a disgusting idol?"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "Should I bow down to dry wood?’"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " He feeds on ashes;"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "his deceived mind misleads him."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "He cannot rescue himself,"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "nor does he say, ‘Is this not a false god I hold in my right hand?’"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " Remember these things, O Jacob,"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "O Israel, for you are my servant."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "I formed you to be my servant;"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "O Israel, I will not forget you!"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " I remove the guilt of your rebellious deeds as if they were a cloud,"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "the guilt of your sins as if they were a cloud."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "  "
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "Come back to me, for I protect"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " you.”"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " Shout for joy, O sky, for "
  },
  {
    "type": "divine_name",
    "value": "YHWH"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " intervenes;"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "shout out, you subterranean regions"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " of the earth."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "O mountains, give a joyful shout;"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "you too, O forest and all your trees!"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "For "
  },
  {
    "type": "divine_name",
    "value": "YHWH"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " protects"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " Jacob;"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "he reveals his splendor through Israel."
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " This is what "
  },
  {
    "type": "divine_name",
    "value": "YHWH"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": ", your protector,"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " says,"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "the one who formed you in the womb:"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "“I am "
  },
  {
    "type": "divine_name",
    "value": "YHWH"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": ", who made everything,"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "who alone stretched out the sky,"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "who fashioned the earth all by myself,"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " who frustrates the omens of the empty talkers"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "and humiliates"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " the omen readers,"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "who overturns the counsel of the wise men"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "and makes their advice"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " seem foolish,"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " who fulfills the oracles of his prophetic servants"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "and brings to pass the announcements"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " of his messengers,"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "who says about Jerusalem,"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " ‘She will be inhabited,’"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "and about the towns of Judah, ‘They will be rebuilt,"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "her ruins I will raise up,’"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " who says to the deep sea, ‘Be dry!"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "I will dry up your sea currents,’ "
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " who commissions"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": " Cyrus, the one I appointed as shepherd"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "to carry out all my wishes"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "and to decree concerning Jerusalem, ‘She will be rebuilt,’"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_start"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_text",
    "value": "and concerning the temple, ‘It will be reconstructed.’”"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph_end"
  }
]